quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  4,66,"N’iyo tuza kubategeka tuti \"Mwiyice cyangwa muve mu mazu yanyu (mwimuke burundu)\", ntabyo bari gukora usibye bake muri bo; nyamara iyo baza gukora ibyo basabwa, byari kuba byiza kuri bo bikanarushaho kubakomeza (mu nzira ya Allah)"
  4,67,"Iyo biza kuba bityo (bakoze ibyo basabwa), rwose twari kubaha ingororano zihambaye ziduturutseho"
  4,68,Kandi twari no kubayobora inzira igororotse
  4,69,"Kandi abumvira Allah n’Intumwa (Muhamadi), abo bazaba bari kumwe (mu ijuru) n’abo Allah yahundagajeho inema ze; (barimo) abahanuzi, abemeye by’ukuri, abaguye ku rugamba baharanira inzira ya Allah ndetse n’intungane. Abo ni bo nshuti nziza"
  4,70,"Izo ni ingabire zituruka kwa Allah, kandi Allah arahagije kuba ari Umumenyi uhebuje"
  4,71,Yemwe abemeye! Mujye mwitonda (mu kwitegura umwanzi); mujye mujya ku rugamba mu matsinda atandukanye cyangwa mugendere hamwe
  4,72,"Mu by’ukuri, muri mwe hari utinda kujya ku rugamba, maze mwagerwaho n’akaga (gutsindwa), akavuga ati \"Rwose Allah yampundagajeho inema (yandinze) kuba ntari kumwe na bo"
  4,73,"Ariko iyo mugezweho n’ingabire ziturutse kwa Allah (intsinzi ), rwose avuga -nk’aho nta rukundo ruri hagati yanyu na we- ati \"Iyo nza kuba hamwe na bo, nari kugira intsinzi ihambaye"
  4,74,"Bityo, babandi bemeye guhara ubuzima bw’isi bakabugurana imperuka (abemera) nibarwane mu nzira ya Allah, kandi urwana mu nzira ya Allah akicwa cyangwa agatsinda, tuzamuhemba ibihembo bihambaye"